      • Circle

        public Circle(int x,
              int y,
              int radius)
        Creates a new instance of a Circle object with the left and right edges of the circle at x - radius and x + radius. The top and bottom edges are at y - radius and y + radius. There is no fill.
        Parameters:
        x - the x coordinate of the circle's center
        y - the y coordinate of the circle's center
        radius - the radius of the circle
